{"title":"Web api history","uid":"ef92ce33f7630db6de42bc09728ad0ae","slug":"2022-10-18history","date":"2022-10-18T08:36:43.000Z","updated":"2022-10-18T08:59:29.717Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2022-10-18history.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h2 id=\"history\"><a href=\"#history\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"history\"></a>history</h2><p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/History\" target=\"_blank\" >https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/History</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"replaceState-不刷新页面\"><a href=\"#replaceState-不刷新页面\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"replaceState 不刷新页面\"></a>replaceState 不刷新页面</h2><p>更改页面参数不刷新页面</p>\n<ul>\n<li>用来存 hash</li>\n<li>用来存页面查询参数</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"/post/2022-10-14useSearchParams\" target=\"_blank\" >&#x2F;post&#x2F;2022-10-14useSearchParams</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"scrollRestoration-滚动恢复属性\"><a href=\"#scrollRestoration-滚动恢复属性\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"scrollRestoration 滚动恢复属性\"></a>scrollRestoration 滚动恢复属性</h2><p><strong>auto</strong><br>将恢复用户已滚动到的页面上的位置。</p>\n<p><strong>manual</strong><br>未还原页上的位置。用户必须手动滚动到该位置</p>\n<p>主要来说下这个东西，直接拿 <a href=\"https://www.runoob.com/\" target=\"_blank\" >《菜鸟教程》</a> 演示</p>\n<img src=\"http://t-blog-images.aijs.top/img/202210181643614.gif\" style=\"width: 800px;max-width: 100%\" />\n\n<h2 id=\"参考链接\"><a href=\"#参考链接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考链接\"></a>参考链接</h2><p><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/History\" target=\"_blank\" >https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/History</a></p>\n","text":"historyhttps://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/History replaceState 不刷新页面更改页面参数不刷新页面 用来存 hash 用来存页面查询参数 &#x2F;post&#x2F;2022-10-14u...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":318,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"前端基础","slug":"前端基础","count":30,"path":"api/categories/前端基础.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"前端基础","slug":"前端基础","count":32,"path":"api/tags/前端基础.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"t